#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles_and_graphics.rst:35
msgid "Titles and Graphics"
msgstr "標題與圖形"

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles_and_graphics.rst:37
msgid ""
"In video production, editing, effects, and compositing are separate steps "
"performed by different roles. But depending on the scope of the production, "
"the size of the team, the editor might also be doing compositing, color "
"grading, video effects, and so on."
msgstr ""
"在影片製作當中，編輯、效果、合成都是分開的步驟，由不同職位所負責。不過依製作"
"規模與團隊大小，編輯者可能也要處理合成、調色 (color grading)、影片效果等等。"

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles_and_graphics.rst:39
msgid ""
"Kdenlive is first and foremost a video editor, not a :abbr:`SFX(Special "
"Effects)` or :abbr:`VFX(Visual Effects)` tool. Nevertheless, it comes with a "
"comprehensive set of :doc:`effects and filters </effects_and_filters>`, :doc:"
"`compositions and transitions </compositing>`, and :doc:`masking tools </"
"compositing/masking_and_tracking>`. For adding texts, titles, graphics and "
"animation, while more a task of the FX department, Kdenlive has its built-"
"in :doc:`Title App</titles_and_graphics/titles/titles>`, and integrates with "
"|glaxnimate| for :doc:`/titles_and_graphics/graphics_and_animations/"
"animations`"
msgstr ""
"Kdenlive 首先是影片編輯器，不是特效（\\ :abbr:`SFX(Special Effects)`\\ ）或視"
"覺效果（\\ :abbr:`VFX(Visual Effects)`\\ ）工具。即便如此，Kdenlive 仍然提供"
"許多\\ :doc:`效果與過濾器 </effects_and_filters>`\\ 、:doc:`合成方案與轉場效"
"果 </compositing>`\\ ，以及\\ :doc:`遮罩工具 </compositing/"
"masking_and_tracking>`\\ 。要加入文字、標題、圖形與動畫，雖然這比較是特效組的"
"工作，但 Kdenlive 仍有提供內建的\\ :doc:`標題工具 </titles_and_graphics/"
"titles/titles>`\\ ，也與 |glaxnimate| 整合提供\\ :doc:`圖形與動畫 </"
"titles_and_graphics/graphics_and_animations/animations>`\\ 。"

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles_and_graphics.rst:41
msgid ""
"For more complex graphics, 3D animations or the like, you need to use "
"specialized applications like |blender|, |inkscape|, |krita|, or |gimp|, and "
"bring their output into Kdenlive just like any other multimedia asset."
msgstr ""
"對於更複雜的圖形與 3D 動畫等等，您會需要使用專門的應用程式，像是 |blender|、|"
"inkscape|、|krita| 或 |gimp|，然後再將它們的輸出如同其他多媒體資源一樣帶進 "
"Kdenlive。"
